data.title: Le roi et la reine de Roumanie et leur escorte (Short 1897)
data.meta_description: Le roi et la reine de Roumanie et leur escorte: With Elisabeth of Wied, King Carol of Romania, King Ferdinand of Romania. Passage of Queen Elisabeth of Wied in a carriage escorted by horsemen, followed by King Charles I and Prince Ferdinand of Hohenzollern on horseback, whom the crowd greets.
